{"content":[{"id":"1147019e","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"4d68bb5c","settings":{"title":"Add Your Heading Text Here","editor":"<div id=\"model-response-message-contentr_8404ea8d17c16c3e\" class=\"markdown markdown-main-panel force-compact-layout enable-updated-hr-color\" dir=\"ltr\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-busy=\"false\"><h1 data-path-to-node=\"3\"><span class=\"citation-6607 citation-6608 citation-6609 citation-6610 citation-6611 citation-6612 citation-6613 citation-end-6613\">Help Center<\/span><\/h1><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-234\" data-path-to-node=\"4\"><span class=\"citation-6600 citation-6601 citation-6602 citation-6603 citation-6604 citation-6605 citation-6606\">Welcome to the <\/span><b data-path-to-node=\"4\" data-index-in-node=\"15\"><span class=\"citation-6600 citation-6601 citation-6602 citation-6603 citation-6604 citation-6605 citation-6606\">LV\u2019s Trendz<\/span><\/b><span class=\"citation-6600 citation-6601 citation-6602 citation-6603 citation-6604 citation-6605 citation-6606 citation-end-6606\"> Help Center. We are dedicated to providing you with the best shopping experience for your favorite ethnic wear. Find quick answers to your questions below.<\/span><\/p><hr data-path-to-node=\"5\" \/><h2 data-path-to-node=\"6\"><span class=\"citation-6593 citation-6594 citation-6595 citation-6596 citation-6597 citation-6598 citation-6599 citation-end-6599\">\ud83d\udecd\ufe0f Orders &amp; Purchasing<\/span><\/h2><h3 data-path-to-node=\"7\"><span class=\"citation-6586 citation-6587 citation-6588 citation-6589 citation-6590 citation-6591 citation-6592 citation-end-6592\">How do I place an order?<\/span><\/h3><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-235\" data-path-to-node=\"8\"><span class=\"citation-6579 citation-6580 citation-6581 citation-6582 citation-6583 citation-6584 citation-6585 citation-end-6585\">Simply browse our collections, select<\/span><span class=\"citation-6579 citation-6580 citation-6581 citation-6582 citation-6583 citation-6584\"> your desired outfit (make sure to check the size guide!), and click <\/span><b data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"106\"><span class=\"citation-6579 citation-6580 citation-6581 citation-6582 citation-6583 citation-6584\">Add to Cart<\/span><\/b><span class=\"citation-6579 citation-6580 citation-6581 citation-6582 citation-6583 citation-6584 citation-end-6584\">. Once you are r<\/span><span class=\"citation-6579 citation-6580 citation-6581 citation-6582 citation-6583\">eady, click on your cart and proceed to <\/span><b data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"173\"><span class=\"citation-6579 citation-6580 citation-6581 citation-6582 citation-6583\">Checkout<\/span><\/b><span class=\"citation-6579 citation-6580 citation-6581 citation-6582 citation-6583 citation-end-6583\"> to enter your shipping and payment details.<\/span><\/p><h3 data-path-to-node=\"9\"><span class=\"citation-6574 citation-6575 citation-6576 citation-6577 citation-6578 citation-end-6578\">Can I change or<\/span><span class=\"citation-6574 citation-6575 citation-6576 citation-6577 citation-end-6577\"> cancel my order after placing it?<\/span><\/h3><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-236\" data-path-to-node=\"10\"><span class=\"citation-6570 citation-6571 citation-6572 citation-6573 citation-end-6573\">We process orders quickly to ensure fast delivery. If you need to make changes<\/span><span class=\"citation-6570 citation-6571 citation-6572\"> or cancel an order, please contact our support team at <\/span><b data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"134\"><span class=\"citation-6570 citation-6571 citation-6572\">lvstrendz.info@gmail.com<\/span><\/b><span class=\"citation-6570 citation-6571 citation-6572 citation-end-6572\"> with<\/span><span class=\"citation-6570 citation-6571\">in <\/span><b data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"166\"><span class=\"citation-6570 citation-6571\">2 hours<\/span><\/b><span class=\"citation-6570 citation-6571 citation-end-6571\"> of placing your order.<\/span><\/p><hr data-path-to-node=\"11\" \/><h2 data-path-to-node=\"12\"><span class=\"citation-6568 citation-6569 citation-end-6569\">\ud83d\ude9a Shipping &amp; Delivery<\/span><\/h2><h3 data-path-to-node=\"13\"><span class=\"citation-6566 citation-6567 citation-end-6567\">Do you ship internati<\/span><span class=\"citation-6566 citation-end-6566\">onally?<\/span><\/h3><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-237\" data-path-to-node=\"14\"><span class=\"citation-6565 citation-end-6565\">Currently, we primar<\/span>ily <span class=\"citation-6564 citation-end-6564\">fulfill domestic orders within India. For special international shipping requests, please get in touch with our customer care team before placing an order.<\/span><\/p><h3 data-path-to-node=\"15\"><span class=\"citation-6563 citation-end-6563\">How long will it take to receive my order?<\/span><\/h3><ul data-path-to-node=\"16\"><li><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-238\" data-path-to-node=\"16,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"16,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span class=\"citation-6562 citation-end-6562\">Standa<\/span>rd Ready-to-Wear Delivery:<\/b> 5 to 7 business days.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"16,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"16,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Custom Size Orders:<\/b> Requires an <b data-path-to-node=\"16,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"32\">additional 5 to 8 business days<\/b> for custom tailoring and processing before dispatch.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"16,1,0\">Tracking details will be emailed to you as soon as your outfit is ready and shipped.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><hr data-path-to-node=\"17\" \/><h2 data-path-to-node=\"18\">\ud83d\udd04 Exchange Policy<\/h2><h3 data-path-to-node=\"19\">What is your return and exchange policy?<\/h3><blockquote data-path-to-node=\"20\"><p data-path-to-node=\"20,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"20,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Important Note:<\/b> We do <b data-path-to-node=\"20,0\" data-index-in-node=\"22\">not<\/b> accept returns or offer refunds. All sales are final. We do not offer exchange in custom size orders.<\/p><\/blockquote><p data-path-to-node=\"21\">However, we happily offer <b data-path-to-node=\"21\" data-index-in-node=\"26\">exchanges only<\/b> under the following strict conditions:<\/p><ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"22\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"22,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"22,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Wrong Size:<\/b> If the outfit does not fit you properly.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"22,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"22,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Defective\/Damaged Piece:<\/b> If the item arrived damaged or with a manufacturing defect.<\/p><\/li><\/ol><h3 data-path-to-node=\"23\">What are the conditions for an exchange?<\/h3><p data-path-to-node=\"24\">To be eligible for an exchange, your item must be requested within <b data-path-to-node=\"24\" data-index-in-node=\"67\">7 days<\/b> of delivery. The item must be unworn, unwashed, with all original tags attached, and in its original packaging. Custom-stitched or custom-sized outfits are entirely excluded from exchanges.<\/p><h3 data-path-to-node=\"25\">How do I initiate an exchange?<\/h3><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-239\" data-path-to-node=\"26\">Please email us at <b data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"19\">lvstrendz.info@gmail.com<\/b> with your <b data-path-to-node=\"26\" data-index-in-node=\"54\">Order ID<\/b> and clear photos\/videos of the defect or size issue. Our customer care team will review your request and guide you through the exchange <span class=\"citation-6561 citation-end-6561\">process.<\/span><\/p><hr data-path-to-node=\"27\" \/><h2 data-path-to-node=\"28\"><span class=\"citation-6560 citation-end-6560\">\ud83d\udccf Sizing &amp; Customization<\/span><\/h2><h3 data-path-to-node=\"29\"><span class=\"citation-6559 citation-end-6559\">How do I choose the correct size?<\/span><\/h3><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-240\" data-path-to-node=\"30\"><span class=\"citation-6558 citation-end-6558\">Every product page includes a detailed size chart. Since ethnic wear like Lehenga Cholis depends heavily on a good fit, we highly recommend measuring your bust, waist, and hips accurately before or<\/span>dering to avoid size exchange hassle.<\/p><h3 data-path-to-node=\"31\">Do you offer custom stitching?<\/h3><p data-path-to-node=\"32\">Yes! Select outfits come with custom sizing options. Please note that choosing a custom size adds <b data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"98\">5 to 8 days<\/b> to our standard processing time so our tailors can ensure a flawless fit. For specific measurement requests, reach out to our team via WhatsApp\/Call at <b data-path-to-node=\"32\" data-index-in-node=\"262\">+91-8780389067<\/b>.<\/p><hr data-path-to-node=\"33\" \/><h2 data-path-to-node=\"34\"><span class=\"citation-6550 citation-6551 citation-6552 citation-6553 citation-6554 citation-6555 citation-6556 citation-6557 citation-end-6557\">\ud83d\udcb3 Payments &amp; Security<\/span><\/h2><h3 data-path-to-node=\"35\"><span class=\"citation-6542 citation-6543 citation-6544 citation-6545 citation-6546 citation-6547 citation-6548 citation-6549 citation-end-6549\">What payment methods do you accept?<\/span><\/h3><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-241\" data-path-to-node=\"36\"><span class=\"citation-6534 citation-6535 citation-6536 citation-6537 citation-6538 citation-6539 citation-6540 citation-6541 citation-end-6541\">We accept a wide range of secure payment options, including:<\/span><\/p><ul data-path-to-node=\"37\"><li><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-242\" data-path-to-node=\"37,0,0\"><span class=\"citation-6526 citation-6527 citation-6528 citation-6529 citation-6530 citation-6531 citation-6532 citation-6533 citation-end-6533\">Credit \/ Debit Cards (Visa, MasterCard, RuPay)<\/span><\/p><\/li><li><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-243\" data-path-to-node=\"37,1,0\"><span class=\"citation-6518 citation-6519 citation-6520 citation-6521 citation-6522 citation-6523 citation-6524 citation-6525 citation-end-6525\">UPI (Google Pay, PhonePe, Paytm)<\/span><\/p><\/li><li><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-244\" data-path-to-node=\"37,2,0\"><span class=\"citation-6510 citation-6511 citation-6512 citation-6513 citation-6514 citation-6515 citation-6516 citation-6517 citation-end-6517\">Net Banking<\/span><\/p><\/li><\/ul><h3 data-path-to-node=\"38\"><span class=\"citation-6502 citation-6503 citation-6504 citation-6505 citation-6506 citation-6507 citation-6508 citation-6509 citation-end-6509\">Is my payment secure?<\/span><\/h3><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-245\" data-path-to-node=\"39\"><span class=\"citation-6494 citation-6495 citation-6496 citation-6497 citation-6498 citation-6499 citation-6500 citation-6501 citation-end-6501\">Absolut<\/span><span class=\"citation-6494 citation-6495 citation-6496 citation-6497 citation-6498 citation-6499 citation-6500 citation-end-6500\">ely. Your online transactions are completely secure. We use industry-standard encryption protocols to protect your financial data and personal informat<\/span><span class=\"citation-6494 citation-6495 citation-6496 citation-6497 citation-6498 citation-6499 citation-end-6499\">ion.<\/span><\/p><hr data-path-to-node=\"40\" \/><h2 data-path-to-node=\"41\"><span class=\"citation-6488 citation-6489 citation-6490 citation-6491 citation-6492 citation-6493 citation-end-6493\">\ud83d\udcde Still Need Help?<\/span><\/h2><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-246\" data-path-to-node=\"42\"><span class=\"citation-6482 citation-6483 citation-6484 citation-6485 citation-6486 citation-6487 citation-end-6487\">If you couldn't find the answer to your question, our customer<\/span><span class=\"citation-6482 citation-6483 citation-6484 citation-6485 citation-6486 citation-end-6486\"> care team is always happy to assist you!<\/span><\/p><ul data-path-to-node=\"43\"><li><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-247\" data-path-to-node=\"43,0,0\"><span class=\"citation-6477 citation-6478 citation-6479 citation-6480 citation-6481\">\ud83d\udce7 <\/span><b data-path-to-node=\"43,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"3\"><span class=\"citation-6477 citation-6478 citation-6479 citation-6480 citation-6481\">Email Us:<\/span><\/b><span class=\"citation-6477 citation-6478 citation-6479 citation-6480 citation-6481 citation-end-6481\"> lvstrendz.inf<\/span><span class=\"citation-6477 citation-6478 citation-6479 citation-6480 citation-end-6480\">o@gmail.com<\/span><\/p><\/li><li><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-248\" data-path-to-node=\"43,1,0\"><span class=\"citation-6473 citation-6474 citation-6475 citation-6476\">\ud83d\udcde <\/span><b data-path-to-node=\"43,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"3\"><span class=\"citation-6473 citation-6474 citation-6475 citation-6476\">Call \/ WhatsApp:<\/span><\/b><span class=\"citation-6473 citation-6474 citation-6475 citation-6476 citation-end-6476\"> +91-8<\/span><span class=\"citation-6473 citation-6474 citation-6475 citation-end-6475\">780389067<\/span><\/p><\/li><li><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-249\" data-path-to-node=\"43,2,0\"><span class=\"citation-6470 citation-6471 citation-6472\">\ud83d\udccd <\/span><b data-path-to-node=\"43,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"3\"><span class=\"citation-6470 citation-6471 citation-6472\">Visit Us:<\/span><\/b><span class=\"citation-6470 citation-6471 citation-6472 citation-end-6472\"> C-301 Bhavani Complex, Nr. Gajera Circ<\/span><span class=\"citation-6470 citation-6471 citation-end-6471\">le, Opp. Saibaba Petrol Pump, Katargam, Surat - 39<\/span><span class=\"citation-6470 citation-end-6470\">5004<\/span><\/p><\/li><li><p id=\"p-rc_d8acfc15639e9c89-250\" data-path-to-node=\"43,3,0\"><span class=\"citation-6469\">\u23f0 <\/span><b data-path-to-node=\"43,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"2\"><span class=\"citation-6469\">Support Hours:<\/span><\/b><span class=\"citation-6469 citation-end-6469\"> Monday to Saturday, 10:00 AM \u2013 7:00 <\/span>PM (IST)<\/p><\/li><\/ul><\/div>"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"bzotech-heading-global","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"container"}],"settings":{"template":"default"},"metadata":[]}